title: #2 - Initial Liquidity Mining
body:
This proposal will approve the Community Treasury to start a preliminary liquidity mining program by creating a 2000🐟 sablier stream from the community treasury to be distributed directly in to the ETH-🐟 LP weekly by the co-delegates calling withdrawFromStream() on the sablier.finance contract from the Treasury multi-sig.

Functions called Now:
- approve(SablierContract,2000🐟);
- createStream(eth-🐟, 2000🐟, 🐟Contract, ASAP, Two months from start) 
 on Sablier.finance contract: 0xA4fc358455Febe425536fd1878bE67FfDBDEC59a

Functions called, ongoing, weekly, for two months:
- withdrawFromStream(fishStream, claimAmount)
author: 0x0be0eCC301a1c0175f07A66243cfF628c24DB852
